---
import { NAV, SITE } from '@/data/site';
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-white/80">
  <div class="section-tight grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr]">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt={`${SITE.name} logo`} class="h-7 w-7 object-contain" />
        </span>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">{SITE.name}</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Viajes personalizados a medida</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
        {SITE.slogan} Pensado para clientes que quieren dejar de improvisar y empezar a viajar con una ruta bien construida.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <a class="hover:text-slate-900" href={SITE.whatsappUrl}>WhatsApp</a>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>Email administrativo: {SITE.email}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{SITE.address}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Explora</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
        {NAV.map((item) => (
          <li>
            <a href={item.href} class="hover:text-slate-900">{item.label}</a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">Legal</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li><a class="hover:text-slate-900" href="/aviso-legal/">Aviso legal</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-slate-900" href="/privacidad/">Privacidad</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-slate-900" href="/cookies/">Cookies</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-slate-900" href="/condiciones-generales/">Condiciones generales</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="section-tight flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-slate-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE.name}. {SITE.legalNote}</p>
      <p>Diseñado para Cloudflare Pages, Netlify o Vercel sin backend obligatorio.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
